		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Oh, I see. So if you want to not have to keep a variable of the vertical scroll for doing the wavy effect, you can just read from $2002 to have it ignore the second write. I didn't know about this. It's good to know if I ever want to do some cool scrolling tricks.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
